### List all distributors
GET http://localhost:3000/api/distributors

# ============================================================================
# SEARCHS
# ============================================================================

### Search by name (default)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/distributors/search?q=Luca

### Search by name (explicit)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/distributors/search?q=Luca&by=name

### Search by zone
GET http://localhost:3000/api/distributors/search?q=Centro&by=zone

### Search by zone - minimum 2 characters
GET http://localhost:3000/api/distributors/search?q=Ce&by=zone

